It began with a follower telling the media personality that men remain the head and women who are not ready to be submissive to a man should remain single.


Controversial OAP and Free The Sheeple Leader, Daddy Freeze has lambasted his followers who insist that the husband is the head of the family so his wife must be submissive to him.
It began with a follower telling Daddy Freeze that men remain the head and women who are not ready to respect or be submissive to a man should remain single.
Freeze told the woman: “Must you marry an African?”
He added: “Why should ‘remain single’ be the only option?”
 
