Another follower then asked Freeze: “Are you saying if a lady marries an oyibo man she shouldn’t be submissive?”
Freeze slammed the follower writing: “Nigeria has trapped hour body bro, don’t let it trap your brain…
“Unlike Nigerians, Oyibo people have partnerships, not ‘master/servant’ relationships.”
